Model Year Start: 2016 Model: Prius Prod Date Range: [11/2015 - 07/2020]
Title: SEAT: FRONT SEAT ASSEMBLY (for Manual Seat): REASSEMBLY; 2016 - 2020 MY Prius [11/2015 - 07/2020]

REASSEMBLY

CAUTION / NOTICE / HINT

CAUTION:

Wear protective gloves. Sharp areas on the parts may injure your hands.

HINT:

  • Use the same procedure for the RH side and LH side.
  • The following procedure is for the LH side.

PROCEDURE

1. INSTALL VERTICAL ADJUSTER BRACKET COVER LH (for Driver Side)

(a) Engage the claw to install the vertical adjuster bracket cover LH to the front vertical adjuster brake sub-assembly LH.

2. INSTALL FRONT SEAT VERTICAL ADJUSTER ASSEMBLY (for Driver Side)

(a) Install the front seat vertical adjuster assembly.

(1) Install the front vertical adjuster brake sub-assembly LH.

NOTICE:

Make sure to insert the stud bolt of the front vertical adjuster brake sub-assembly LH into the hole of the front seat adjuster assembly as shown in the illustration.

(2) Install the vertical adjuster spacer.

(3) Install the vertical adjuster plate with the 3 nuts.

Torque:

5.0 Nm {51 kgfcm, 44 inlbf}

NOTICE:

Tighten the nuts in the order shown in the illustration.

3. INSTALL SEAT TRACK ADJUSTING HANDLE

(a) Engage the 2 claws to install the seat track adjusting handle to the front seat adjuster assembly.

4. INSTALL FRONT SEAT CUSHION SPRING SUB-ASSEMBLY

(a) Engage the 6 hooks to install the front seat cushion spring sub-assembly to the front seat adjuster assembly.

5. INSTALL FRONT SEAT CUSHION WIRE HARNESS HOLDER

(a) Engage the claw to install the front seat cushion wire harness holder.

(b) Install the 2 screws.

6. INSTALL FRONT SEAT WIRE RH (for Front Passenger Side)

(a) Connect each connector and engage each clamp to install the front seat wire RH.

7. INSTALL FRONT SEAT LOWER CUSHION SHIELD LH (for Driver Side)

(a) Engage the claw and guide to install the front seat lower cushion shield LH.

*a

Hook

*b

Guide

(b) Engage the hook.

8. INSTALL FRONT SEAT LOWER CUSHION SHIELD RH (for Driver Side)

(a) Engage the claw and guide to install the front seat lower cushion shield RH.

*a

Hook

*b

Guide

(b) Engage the hook.

9. INSTALL LH SEAT RECLINING ADJUSTER INSIDE COVER LH (for Driver Side)

(a) Engage the 4 claws to install the LH seat reclining adjuster inside cover LH.

10. INSTALL LH SEAT RECLINING ADJUSTER INSIDE COVER RH (for Driver Side)

HINT:

Use the same procedure as for the LH side.

11. INSTALL RH SEAT RECLINING ADJUSTER INSIDE COVER LH (for Front Passenger Side)

(a) Engage the 4 claws to install the RH seat reclining adjuster inside cover LH.

(b) Engage the clamp.

12. INSTALL RH SEAT RECLINING ADJUSTER INSIDE COVER RH (for Front Passenger Side)

(a) Engage the 4 claws to install the RH seat reclining adjuster inside cover RH.

13. INSTALL FRONT SEAT CUSHION AIRBAG ASSEMBLY RH (for Front Passenger Side)

Click here

14. INSTALL FRONT SEAT CUSHION HEATER ASSEMBLY (w/ Seat Heater System)

Click here

15. INSTALL SEPARATE TYPE FRONT SEAT CUSHION COVER

(a) Engage the 13 claws to install the separate type front seat cushion cover to the separate type front seat cushion pad.

16. INSTALL SEPARATE TYPE FRONT SEAT CUSHION COVER WITH PAD

(a) Engage the 10 hooks to install the separate type front seat cushion cover with pad.

(b) Engage the 2 hooks.

(c) w/ Seat Heater System:

(1) Engage the claw and 4 clamps to install the front seat cushion heater assembly wire harness.

HINT:

Engage the claw first.

17. INSTALL FRONT SEATBACK HOOK

(a) Install the 2 front seatback hooks to the front seatback frame sub-assembly.

18. INSTALL FRONT SEATBACK EDGE PROTECTOR

(a) Install the 2 front seatback edge protectors to the front seatback spring sub-assembly.

19. INSTALL FRONT SEATBACK SPRING SUB-ASSEMBLY

(a) Install the front seatback spring sub-assembly to the front seatback frame sub-assembly as shown in the illustration.

Install in this direction

(b) Engage the 2 claws to install the 2 front seatback edge protectors to the front seatback frame sub-assembly.

20. INSTALL FRONT SEAT AIRBAG ASSEMBLY

Click here

21. INSTALL FRONT SEATBACK HEATER ASSEMBLY (w/ Seat Heater System)

Click here

22. INSTALL SEPARATE TYPE FRONT SEATBACK COVER

(a) Engage the 18 claws to install the separate type front seatback cover to the separate type front seatback pad.

23. INSTALL SEPARATE TYPE FRONT SEATBACK COVER WITH PAD

(a) Install the separate type front seatback cover with pad.

24. INSTALL FRONT SEAT HEADREST SUPPORT

(a) Engage the 4 claws to install the 2 front seat headrest supports.

(b) Close the 2 fasteners.

(c) w/ Seat Heater System:

(1) Engage the clamp.

(d) Engage the 3 hooks.

25. INSTALL SEPARATE TYPE FRONT SEATBACK ASSEMBLY

(a) Engage the 4 guides.

(b) Install the separate type front seatback assembly to the separate type front seat cushion assembly with the 4 bolts.

Torque:

42 Nm {428 kgfcm, 31 ftlbf}

(c) Engage the claw and 4 clamps to install the front seat airbag assembly wire harness.

HINT:

Engage the claw first.

(d) w/ Seat Heater System:

(1) Engage the clamp.

(2) Connect the connector.

(e) Engage the 2 hooks.

(f) Pass the separate type front seatback cover through the grooves of the LH seat reclining adjuster inside cover LH and LH seat reclining adjuster inside cover RH.

26. INSTALL FRONT SEAT INNER CUSHION SHIELD LH (for Driver Side)

(a) Engage the 2 claws and 2 guides as shown in the illustration.

Install in this direction

(b) Engage the 2 claws to install the front seat inner cushion shield LH.

27. INSTALL FRONT SEAT CUSHION SHIELD LH (for Driver Side)

(a) Engage the guide (A) as shown in the illustration.

Install in this direction (1)

Install in this direction (2)

(b) Engage the 3 claws and 2 guides (B) as shown in the illustration.

(c) Engage the 2 claws to install the front seat cushion shield LH.

28. INSTALL SEAT ADJUSTER COVER CAP (for Driver Side)

(a) Engage the 2 guides as shown in the illustration.

Install in this direction (1)

Install in this direction (2)

(b) Engage the 2 claws to install the seat adjuster cover cap as shown in the illustration.

29. INSTALL FRONT SEAT INNER CUSHION SHIELD RH (for Front Passenger Side)

(a) Engage the 2 claws and 2 guides as shown in the illustration.

Install in this direction

(b) Engage the 3 claws to install the front seat inner cushion shield RH.

30. INSTALL FRONT SEAT CUSHION SHIELD RH (for Front Passenger Side)

(a) Engage the guide (A) as shown in the illustration.

Install in this direction (1)

Install in this direction (2)

(b) Engage the 2 claws and 2 guides (B) as shown in the illustration.

(c) Engage the 2 claws to install the front seat cushion shield RH.

31. INSTALL RECLINING ADJUSTER RELEASE HANDLE

(a) Install the reclining adjuster release handle.

32. INSTALL NO. 1 RECLINING HINGE COVER

(a) Engage the guide.

(b) Engage the claw to install the No. 1 reclining hinge cover.

33. INSTALL VERTICAL ADJUSTING HANDLE (for Driver Side)

(a) Engage the claw to install the vertical adjusting handle as shown in the illustration.

Install in this direction

34. CONNECT SEPARATE TYPE FRONT SEATBACK COVER

(a) Connect the rubber band of the separate type front seatback cover.
